Usage: reportShield [-help] [-crosstie] [-include_layer] [-out_file <filename>]
                    [-selected] [-tap_cells] [-verbose]

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-crosstie                                 # crosstie (bool, optional)
-include_layer                            # include layer (bool, optional)
-out_file <filename>                      # out file name (string, optional)
-selected                                 # -selected for selected nets
                                          # (bool, optional)
-tap_cells                                # tap_cells (bool, optional)
-verbose                                  # verbose (bool, optional)